
        Usage: manga -s <path>

> by default pdf file will be saved in the current directory  

Arguments : 

-v, --version            get current version
-h, --help               give this help list
-i, --issue              give the url to issue page
-d, --documentation      give the url to documentation page
-s, --save               set download path(optional)(by default pdf file will be saved in the current working directory)
-r, --remove             remove thanks page(optional)
